response.original_title: Falls ich es schaffe oder Pardon my donkey thumbs
response.overview: Eight minutes directly after the apocalypse. As though concocted in a test tube, Falls ich es schaffe oder Pardon my donkey thumbs“ muses about the senselessness of all ambition, saws into, mills along, nuzzles up to the eye and the synapses that are forced to surrender in the face of formal eclecticism. That is not necessarily bad, as the prize is often under the trash can.“ (Diagonale 2017 Catalogue)
